HEADWORD: Lappish
<hw>Lap"pish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
the Lapps; Laplandish.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>The language
spoken by the Lapps in Lapland. It is related to the Finnish and
Hungarian, and is not an Aryan language.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
